6 An Act relating to emergency management; amending 63
O.S. 2021, Sections 683.8 and 683.9, which relate to
7 powers and duties of Governor and natural or man-made
emergencies; prohibiting Governor from closing
8 businesses under certain circumstances; requiring
certain evidence for authorized closure; requiring
9 due process for businesses ordered to close; defining
term; updating statutory reference; providing an
10 effective date; and declaring an emergency.
11
