13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 63 O.S. 2021, Section 683.8, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 683.8. A. The Governor shall have general direction
17 and control of the Oklahoma Department of Emergency Management and
18 shall be responsible for carrying out the provisions of the Oklahoma
19 Emergency Management Act of 2003. In the event of an emergency that
20 exceeds local capability, the Governor may assume direct operational
21 control over all or any part of the emergency management functions
22 within this state.
23 B. The Governor shall have general direction and control of
24 emergency management within the state and all officers, boards,
